{"tid":131373,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁樣餵主人食野會唔會太多？","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T10:59:12.000Z","uid":8471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a4afa94dbc5e097114f43d9bc5a611f3fd031e","tid":131373,"uid":8471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"我照早六點六起身返工就餵呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/123545_4441d6c1ea622a086261ab36effe5da1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F123545_4441d6c1ea622a086261ab36effe5da1.jpg&h=90ff39ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住夜晚十點半到就餵呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/123634_c32765f33c66495b7576a0c33e09d73f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F123634_c32765f33c66495b7576a0c33e09d73f.jpg&h=2899e335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照早果罐係156g 夜晚果罐係85g<br />\n味道就幾隻味輪住換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/123843_199690d9a151acda6f86405a20ce4919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F123843_199690d9a151acda6f86405a20ce4919.jpg&h=4f0e95b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc207d445db3067cd43531e740ae1ce6bd94162","tid":131373,"uid":8471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:40:29.000Z","msg":"重有長期放左乾糧係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35a47258d733a1519d686f41033a1f18e0aec75","tid":131373,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"你有冇覺得濟？"},{"pid":"06a92e8e9b5d607628aa9f05fb0fd99d91677982","tid":1